content: # I understand we can use Slack to make calls at anytime. How do I do that now that I downloaded the app?
I'm going bring this to the attention of <@1271505055589339207> who manages the calls team.
(Slack is a chat platform, which has a channel to support phonebankers.  It's not the dialer.)  The training for calling is at https://events.democrats.org/event/551644/
